{
  "texts": [
    "The extent of the numerical domain along the streamwise, lateral, and axial directions is x/d ∈ [0, 24], y/d ∈ [0, 20], and z/d ∈ [0, π], respectively.",
    "The cylinder is placed at x/d = 8 and y/d = 10.",
    "The block-structured mesh consists of 9.416 • 10 6 hexahedral cells.",
    "The incompressible simulation is executed using OpenFOAM-v2206 [5].",
    "For more information on the numerical setup and the flow physics, we refer to [16]."
  ]
}